text: Ex-Google chief claims new venture will hit £1bn-turnover 'unicorn' status Dan Cobley claims he can to solve the money worries of the nation's workers with start-up, SalaryFinance Dan Cobley, former boss of Google UK, is launching a fintech venture By Rebecca Burn-Callander , Enterprise Editor 10:23PM BST 20 Sep 2015
